    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "―― 一月二十五日　朝",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "始まりました、『ⅢX公式ch』！\n早速ですが、今回のゲストはこちらの方です",
      "startTime": 6.4333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3801.1563381,
          "startTime": 10.2344896714
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "こんにちは～！　スタンプラリーは人生！\n月のテンペストの白石沙季です！",
      "startTime": 13.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "カット。今、スタンプラリーは関係ないわよね？\nのっけから悪いのだけれど、変えてちょうだい",
      "startTime": 20.8473017692,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_switch-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 16.1962809641
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ！？　あ、あの……私の定番の挨拶なのですが……\nそ、そうですね、お邪魔する立場なので変えてみます",
      "startTime": 29,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "始まりました、『ⅢX公式ch』！\n早速ですが、今回のゲストを紹介します",
      "startTime": 38.3758501688,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3548.7973291999992,
          "startTime": 41.924647498
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "こんにちは～！　ⅢXは人生！　月のテンペストの\n白石沙季です！　よろしくお願いしましゅ！",
      "startTime": 46.4,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_switch-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4984.806831500002,
          "startTime": 51.3848068315
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "カット！　グループ名を続けて言うと分かり辛いわ\n妙なごますりも鼻につく。それと噛んでいたわよね",
      "startTime": 55.6815197307,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "（うぅ、パフォーマンスを教えてもらう企画なのに）\n（挨拶だけで凄いリテイク……。でも、これも勉強よね）",
      "startTime": 64.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "うん、沙季はもともと上手だし、飲み込みが早いわね\nそれじゃあ、このまま練習を続けましょうか",
      "startTime": 79.1403635023,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "（やっぱり、パフォーマンスに関しては勉強になるわ）\n（カメラの前だと、雰囲気も柔らかいし）",
      "startTime": 86.6850783081,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "でも、あまり調子に乗らないでちょうだいね\nお遊戯会よりはマシになったけど、まだまだ甘いわ",
      "startTime": 93.9561457632,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "はい、分かり……って、あの、mihoさん？\nカメラが回っているので、その発言はイメージが……",
      "startTime": 102.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫、ここは音声は使わないわ。表情を映して\nナレーションやテロップを被せるつもりだから",
      "startTime": 112.4149954477,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そういう編集プランなんですね。あ、あはは……\nそれなら、私も笑っておこうかな～、あはは……",
      "startTime": 120.6547586137,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "こんなところね。約束どおり、ゲスト出演のかわりに\n練習を見てあげたし、文句ないでしょう",
      "startTime": 132.7405060767,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、他のカバーメンバーに教えるよりは良かったわ\nちょうど沙季は、私のパートを担当するみたいだし",
      "startTime": 140.4405060767,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "厳しく教えていただき、ありがとうございました\nすずちゃん達にも、今日のことを伝えておきますね",
      "startTime": 147.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに厳しくされるのが好きだなんて、妙な趣味ね\n場合によっては、泣かれると思っていたのだけれど",
      "startTime": 155.41887331,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そういう趣味な訳ではないんですが……。私が妥協\nすれば、妥協したものが皆さんに届いてしまいます",
      "startTime": 162.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "それは不誠実ですし、誰のためにもなりません\n厳しさを受け止め、良いものを届ける方が私は好きです",
      "startTime": 171.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "そう。なら足りないのは経験ね。貴方って、見るからに\n苦労するタイプのアイドルだけれど……ま、悪くないわ",
      "startTime": 182.4004281679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "あ……ありがとうございます！　そうだ、今日お誕生日\nでしたよね。実は、プレゼントを用意しているんです",
      "startTime": 193.9666798909,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01-mhk012.m4a",
      "text": "私に？　受け取りはするけれど……\n待って。確かに……それはそれで撮れ高があるわね",
      "startTime": 203.3901770273,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_01-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "動画で使っていただけるんですか！？\nふふっ、嬉しいです。とっておきのお洋服なんですよ",
      "startTime": 211.6666778564,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}